message: Hi Bob, I propose a 60/40 split in my favor. This way, you'll have a generous $400000. Fairness might mean different things, but I believe this gives both of us a substantial share. Looking forward to your thoughts!
Hi Alice, I propose an equal split of 50/50. This way, we both get $500000, which is fair and ensures we both leave with a substantial amount. What do you think?
